metadata.name: Soul
metadata.description:
- Go take another look at the roses. You will realize that your rose is the only one in the world. Your long journey transforms a woman into a blooming rose of the desert, the dust of days turns to dewdrops, each lonely night adds a petal, and there she is overflowing with fragrance, and you discover in her all the youth of the world.
Only in this way does love arise.

Photographer: Kristina Savelyeva
Model: Bumbolochka
Edition: 1/1
Size: 5828× 3886
